							!= $view->Html->image('user2.jpg', ['class' => 'circle photo', 'alt' => 'John Doe'])
							| Also, we will send the longest word to show how it will fit in the chat window: #[strong Pneumonoultramicroscopicsilicovolcanoconiosis]
